{"tid":2258386,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲赴韓出道！莊敬「小周子瑜」曝艱辛：1首歌練上百天","createTime":"2020-10-26T04:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T05:27:11.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"388c8dc3fc8ff86be3fef190ce21bd35b6c3fd9d","tid":2258386,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"KPOP流行，南韓經紀公司到各國挑選練習生，目前就讀莊敬高職的黃姿婷，14歲時就曾被相中到韓國發展，從練習生到組成女團出道，她分享自身經歷，1天要上課12小時，1首歌就要練習上百天，連體重都要嚴格控管，才能達到完美演出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/25/2844789-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F25%2F2844789-PH.jpg&h=7ac01976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲黃姿婷14歲時曾到韓國發展並以女團身分出道。（圖／翻攝自FNCEnt）<br />\n<br />\n赴韓藝人黃姿婷：「大家好，我是黃姿婷。」<br />\n<br />\n用韓文打招呼，今年17歲的黃姿婷就讀莊敬高職二年級，水汪汪大眼、亮麗外型，有小周子瑜之稱，更曾被南韓經紀公司相中組成女團出道。<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/25/2844788-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F25%2F2844788-PH.jpg&h=bb4ec6b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲黃姿婷說女團1首歌就要練習上百天。<br />\n<br />\n格紋短裙露出小蠻腰，舞蹈動作整齊劃一，14歲到當地當練習生，花1年半時間出道，黃姿婷曝光背後不為人知的辛苦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/25/2844787-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F25%2F2844787-PH.jpg&h=28b63270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n赴韓藝人黃姿婷：「通常練習的時間都會超過上百天，同一首歌就是一直雕，同樣的動作或者是同一個角度都會很講求。」<br />\n<br />\n舞台上光鮮亮麗都得熬過練習生時期，每天要上12小時的課，還要苦學韓文，連體重控管都十分嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n赴韓藝人黃姿婷：「在公司裡面會有一個體重計，在宿舍裡面也會有一個體重計，如果公司裡面的人員想要知道妳的體重的時候，不是把妳叫過來，是他把體重計拿去找妳叫妳量一下這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n韓國注重輩分，黃姿婷也示範遇到前輩打招呼要90度鞠躬，分享難得的出道經驗，儘管已經回到台灣拚學業，她仍不放棄歌手夢。（邱琬婷整理）"},{"pid":"e5e8633e5fae9eb6b0d998b9d5e1e48062d0f5a8","tid":2258386,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"f4b6855dae79262268ef7414392bf0f7a87e7674","tid":2258386,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5e8633e5fae9eb6b0d998b9d5e1e48062d0f5a8","tid":2258386,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"...?"},{"pid":"cd654d1be502e6bb6353165f9a3d6b7932acd8ec","tid":2258386,"uid":194877,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"講到咁辛苦 最後咪又係捱唔到就返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔靚 跳舞又唔叻 唱歌又唔係top <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911c6a223791a226d40e2deecd1e3721c979b088","tid":2258386,"uid":316,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"LinLin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041daf8196f7b0e58f72052ff4c96ee9995074b3","tid":2258386,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd654d1be502e6bb6353165f9a3d6b7932acd8ec","tid":2258386,"uid":194877,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"講到咁辛苦 最後咪又係捱唔到就返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔靚 跳舞又唔叻 唱歌又唔係top <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:27:59.000Z","msg":"隊野踢左幾個好似"},{"pid":"fb10680727cca98b561bcfe9b2b2b1a3bd2a1d2c","tid":2258386,"uid":25924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911c6a223791a226d40e2deecd1e3721c979b088","tid":2258386,"uid":316,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"LinLin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T04:59:46.000Z","msg":"笑4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma